A4.text: The title 'Suite: Judy Blue Eyes' is a play on words for 'Sweet Judy Blue Eyes', referring to Stephen Stills' former girlfriend, singer/songwriter Judy Collins.

A5.text: The lyrics to most of the suite's sections consist of his thoughts about her and their imminent breakup.
